<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3492311">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3492311/" class="title-link">通经史，和众声</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3492311"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/iheyou/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u34347548-22.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/iheyou/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">何有</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-01"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-01 22:23:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3492311_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  钱先生说：“若真求学问，则必遵轨道，重师法，求系统，务专门，而后始可谓之真学问。”（145页）而先生此书，也正是在指出一条通往学术罗马之坦途大道。  何谓“学龠”？学不必言，所谓“龠”，《说文解字》解释为“樂之竹管，三孔，以和眾聲也。”可见，“学龠”之矢的，在乎...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3492311/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3492311_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3492311_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5472229">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5472229/" class="title-link">启龠见书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5472229"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/pgsport/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u48503776-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pgsport/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">pgsport</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-06-19"
      class="main-meta">2012-06-19 20:10:08</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5472229_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  学龠：意为学习的钥匙。为钱穆先生关于治学方法与门径的著述，内容有钱先生所谈本人治学方法和感触，以及对古人读书方法和学术源流的介绍。好学之士，细细品读，取而为法，可得为学入门之途径。  虽然儒家是糟粕之学，不深究细品，理解起意即可。一家之言无需拍砖。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5472229_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5472229_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










